{"tid":1914050,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[選項] [重甜] 我參加咗個性交遊戲比賽","createTime":"2020-03-07T08:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T17:22:49.000Z","uid":20285,"like":5,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9880aa774de6ad16374970636e71db8c4031c2","tid":1914050,"uid":20285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:58:07.000Z","msg":"電視台有一個性交遊戲比賽嘅真人Show節目，現正接受報名。<br />\n<br />\n呢個節目已經準備開拍第二季啦，上一季嘅收視非常之高，節目內容大約係幾對男女玩吓鹹濕遊戲，做吓愛雜交吓咁，好多夫妻同情侶都話想去玩吓...<br />\n<br />\n我非常之咁想參加，因為我呢世人冇乜長處，淨係對扑嘢有啲自信，但參賽者必須為一男一女咁一Pair人參加。<br />\n<br />\n但我孤身寡佬，去邊度搵條女同我一參加呢個比賽好？<br />\n<br />\nA. 中學時期嘅一個四眼師妹<br />\nB. 飲嘢識嘅涉臨絶種MK妹<br />\nC. 舊公司有兩分姿色嘅港女<br />\nD. 幫襯過幾次嘅援交妹<br />\nE. 分咗手幾年嘅前度女朋友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返黎睇邊個最多"},{"pid":"9cd88b38245960eeefb131f7c7b147ea6b4dc8ca","tid":1914050,"uid":189068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:58:44.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"8cc2fe8c64c58a70bd52bdffce8fb0d99ce78d06","tid":1914050,"uid":283740,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:00:45.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"6fa3993cf688fa01db517f55aa34d930e3bfbd3e","tid":1914050,"uid":90034,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"D"},{"pid":"6e62dc0f3394718d6403d0a952a934f077d8f660","tid":1914050,"uid":279909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:02:56.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"26524d33c587ed9fc48d6f24494a15ed3b6b061f","tid":1914050,"uid":61918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"384324c9e7f8c2291c73da05a8093b322239aa96","tid":1914050,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:12:42.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"9da6bcc2de6f6d689dab4d03afe5e44532f4ee0d","tid":1914050,"uid":259557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"26dcbc663d41a1c7c3a45359a74b3a32dd0a8343","